Wheeljack-X::

Seeing Nightlight in a spot of trouble, Jackie zings over to help 
out, ramming into Destructor from behind in an attempt to break up 
the "catfight".  With his internal repairs complete, he shifts over 
to robot mode, ready for more mayhem.

Gatara/Jayde/Riekan::

With their original target destroyed, the Rogues now seek a new one.  
Seeing Tyreal in the open is a great invitation for them, and they 
launch a new concentrated barrage against him.  Again, their cloaking 
shields are disrupted by the discharge, and again, they take evasive 
action while the cloak re-establishes itself.
